<paragraph id="IFRS03_32" base="F4230351" principles="yes"><paranum>32</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 3"/><data name="paranum" value="32"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS03_P0134">The <xref base="F4230833" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0297">acquirer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0005"/></ph></xref> shall recognise <xref base="F4230858" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0311">goodwill<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0147"/></ph></xref> as of the <xref base="F4230836" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0298">acquisition date<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0006"/></ph></xref> measured as the excess of (a) over (b) below:</p><ol id="IFRS03_L0016" base="F4230354" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0135" base="F4230355">the aggregate of:</p> <ol id="IFRS03_L0017" base="F4230358" type="lower-roman"><li><li_value>(i)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0136" base="F4230359">the consideration transferred measured in accordance with this IFRS, which generally requires acquisition&#x2011;date <xref base="F16141310" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0309">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> (see <xref id="IFRS03_X0221" base="F5310269" href="IFRS03_37.dita#IFRS03_37">paragraph 37</xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(ii)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0137" base="F4230362">the amount of any <xref base="F4230876" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0323">non&#x2011;controlling interest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0260"/></ph></xref> in the <xref base="F4230829" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0296">acquiree<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0004"/></ph></xref> measured in accordance with this IFRS; and</p> </li><li><li_value>(iii)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0139" base="F4230365">in a <xref base="F4230842" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0304">business combination<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0025"/></ph></xref> achieved in stages (see <xref id="IFRS03_X0223" base="F5310270" href="IFRS03_g41-42A.dita#IFRS03_g41-42A">paragraphs 41 and 42</xref>), the acquisition&#x2011;date fair value of the acquirer&#x2019;s previously held <xref base="F4230851" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0308">equity interest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0104"/></ph></xref> in the acquiree.</p></li></ol></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS03_P0140" base="F4230368">the net of the acquisition&#x2011;date amounts of the <xref base="F4230861" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0314">identifiable<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0174"/></ph></xref> assets acquired and the liabilities assumed measured in accordance with this IFRS.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>